title: President of the Republic receives ambassadors from different countries
text: The President of the Republic, Mr. Abdelmadjid Tebboune, received on Wednesday the Ambassadors of the Islamic Republic of Mauritania Mr. Boulah Ould Mogueye, of Romania Mr. Marcel Alexander, and of the Republic of Korea Mr. Lee Eunyong, who paid him a farewell visit at the end of their respective missions in Algeria.
